## Supabase Configuration
## Get your keys from: https://app.supabase.com/project/_/settings/api
## 1. Create a new project at https://app.supabase.com
## 2. Go to Project Settings > API
## 3. Copy the Project URL and Publishable Key (starts with sb_publishable_)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url_here
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_publishable_key_here

## Gated reports — server-side signed URL minting (used by Netlify Function)
## Service role key, NEVER expose to the client. Set in Netlify env vars for prod.
SUPABASE_URL=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

## Tempmail Checker (disposable email validation - used by Netlify Function)
# Required: API key from https://tempmailchecker.com/dashboard
TEMPMAIL_CHECKER_API_KEY=
# Optional: override base URL (defaults to https://tempmailchecker.com)
TEMPMAIL_CHECKER_BASE_URL=
